                    class="hidden md:block text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#3f3f40] mx-8 text-center wow animate__animated animate__zoomIn mb-3 md:mb-4">
                    2. Choose Good Food for Your Dog
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-[#3f3f40] text-sm md:text-base text-justify">Dogs need to eat healthy
                    and balanced meals, and they should always have fresh water available.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-[#3f3f40] text-sm md:text-base text-justify">The person you're getting
                    the dog from will let you know what food they're giving. But it's a good idea to ask your vet or a
                    nutritionist for advice, just in case the current food might not be the best.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-[#3f3f40] text-sm md:text-base text-justify">
                    Even if you decide to change your dog's food, do it slowly. Make sure to buy the food they're used
                    to until you've talked to your vet. This helps your dog adjust to the new food without any tummy
                    troubles.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mr-0 md:mr-16 wow animate__animated animate__slideInLeft"> <img src="assets/2_dog_welfare.png"
                    alt="" class="w-[220px] md:w-[358px] mb-7 md:mb-0 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl shadow-black"></div>
            <h2
                class="block md:hidden text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#3f3f40] mx-8 text-center wow animate__animated animate__zoomIn mb-5 md:mb-10 ">
                2. Choose Good Food for Your Dog
            </h2>
        </div>

        <!--point 3 - cat -->
        <div
            class="bg-[#fbf8f7] flex flex-col-reverse space-y-8 md:space-y-0 md:flex-row justify-center space-x-0 md:space-x-16 items-center py-0 md:py-14 px-2 md:px-6 ">
            <div class="flex flex-col align-middle w-[80%] md:w-[50%] text-justify">
                <h2
                    class="hidden md:block text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#3f3f40] text-center wow animate__animated animate__zoomIn mb-3 md:mb-4 ">
                    3. Get Toys and Games for Your Dog
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-[#3f3f40] text-sm md:text-base text-justify">Dogs need to do things that
                    make them feel like dogs, such as walking, playing, and chasing (but not too wild!).
                </p>
                <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-[#3f3f40] text-sm md:text-base text-justify">
                    When your dog comes home, having toys and games for them is important. It keeps them happy, active,
                    and thinking. Plus, it's a fun way for both of you to become good friends. Remember, they still need
                    their regular walks, too!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-center items-center wow animate__animated animate__slideInRight">
