                    class="hidden md:block text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#3f3f40] text-center wow animate__animated animate__zoomIn mb-3 md:mb-4 ">
                    5. Register with a vet
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-[#3f3f40] text-sm md:text-base text-justify">The very first and super
                    important thing to do for your dog is to sign up with a vet. This helps make sure your dog stays
